<p>This is a single player air-fight based game built on Unity3D platform. The scripts were written in C# language using Microsoft Visual Studio</p>

<p>This game comprises of two modes-</p>
<ul>
  <li><strong>Arcade Mode:</strong> The war is fought on three battle ground. One has to lead his forces through all these battlegrounds to lead his forces to victory.
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Desert</strong>
  <img src="https://github.com/JitenDhawan/Windows-Game/blob/master/p1.PNG?raw=true" alt="" /></li>
      <li><strong>Hills</strong>
  <img src="https://github.com/JitenDhawan/Windows-Game/blob/master/p2.PNG?raw=true" alt="" /></li>
      <li><strong>Icy Mountains</strong>
  <img src="https://github.com/JitenDhawan/Windows-Game/blob/master/p3.PNG?raw=true" alt="" /></li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>Survival Mode:</strong> In this one has to survive in the battlefield as long as he can. However, battleground doesnâ€™t change.</li>
</ul>

<p>Received a <strong>Special Mention</strong> during the Science &amp; Technology Summer Camp 2016.</p>

